data.description: Welcome to this solar powered stunning  3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers perfect living space with a pool and a bonus unit, perfect for an office or rental opportunity. The exterior offers new dual pane windows and a new AC unit. As you enter the  the court yard step into a spacious living area, ideal for entertaining or relaxing. The open-concept and fully remodeled kitchen features wood shaker cabinets, gold hardware,  modern appliances, plenty of counter space, and an 8ft island.The master bedroom is a true retreat, with a private en-suite bathroom that is fully remodeled  with convenient access to the backyard. Two additional bedrooms offer ample space. Outside, you'll find your own private paradise. The sparkling pool is perfect for cooling off on hot days and surrounded by 2 large covered patio with a built-in BBQ for entertaining. Another great feature this home offers is the bonus unit. Whether you use it as a home office, a guest suite, or a rental opportunity, this versatile space adds incredible value to the property in addition to the detached garage. Located in a desirable neighborhood, close to shops, restaurants, and schools, this home offers the perfect blend of luxury and convenience. Don't Miss Your Chance To Make This Your Forever Home!
